these suggestions.</context>
<steps-unordered class="- topic/ul task/steps-unordered " xtrf="C:\Users\sim\Dropbox (SIM University)\Leon\Backup\DITA\tasks\maintainstorage.dita" xtrc="steps-unordered:1;20:18">
<step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="C:\Users\sim\Dropbox (SIM University)\Leon\Backup\DITA\tasks\maintainstorage.dita" xtrc="step:1;21:7"><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="C:\Users\sim\Dropbox (SIM University)\Leon\Backup\DITA\tasks\maintainstorage.dita" xtrc="cmd:1;21:12">If your drive has a low-power mode, make sure this comes on when
